53222.「ただいまより 第１回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加する:
Now it's time to introduce you to the
beautiful women who will be participating in
the 1st Annual Astrutia Queen Contest!

53223.「オーグリード大陸に咲く 一輪の赤いバラ！\n どんな豪傑も 気安く近づけば返り:
A single red rose blooming in Ogreed Continent! Any man who approaches her with impunity will be struck down! A woman of power
and beauty...

53225.「こんな盛大なイベントに参加できて 光栄だわ。\n 強敵ばかりだけど これは 真:
I'm honored to be a part of such a grand event. I know I'm up against some tough competition, but this is serious business...
and I'm going to make sure I win the title of queen!

53226.「風の町アズランに ひっそりと咲く 月見草！\n その つぶらな瞳は 見る者をと:
The moonflower blooms quietly in Wind Town
Azlan! Its dull eyes captivate all who see
them! The idol of Azlantelope...

53228.「お父さまが 勝手に応募しちゃったけど\n わ…私なんかが 勝てるのかな？\n:
Your father took the liberty of entering the
contest, but... do you think I can win? It's
so embarrassing for everyone to see.

53229.「あたしのゼニは あたしの物！\n あんたのゼニも あたしの物！\n その若さに:
My money is mine! Your money is mine, too!
You're a miser of all misers for such a young
man...

53230.「お金大好きガール ジェニャ！: Jenya, the girl who loves money!

53231.「こら！ お金のことしか言ってないで！: Hey! You're only talking about money!

53232.「てへへっ。あたしを クイーンにしたってや。\n クイーンになって この城を も:
Heh heh. Make me a queen. I want to be queen
and get this castle. So, I'll rent out the
castle, and for a fee...

53233.「こら！ まだ 言い終わってないで！: Hey! You didn't finish your sentence!

53234.「ウェナ諸島に平安をもたらす 美しきディーバ！\n その歌声に ウェディたちはメ:
A beautiful diva who brings peace to the Wena Islands! The sound of her voice is enough to send Weddie and his friends into a frenzy. I
never thought I'd see the real Queen...

53236.「クイーン コンテストと聞いては\n わらわが参加しないワケには いくまい。\n:
When I hear of a queen contest, I can't help
but enter. You must know the majesty of a real
queen.

53237.「岳都ガタラを駆け抜ける 黒い影！\n 今夜のエモノは あなたのハート！\n 天:
A black shadow runs through Mount Gatara!
Tonight's prize is your heart! Know the
heavens! Earth knows! Only a person knows...

53238.「美少女怪盗ポイックリン！\n 華麗に 参上でございますわっ！:
Phantom Thief Poiclin! Here she comes in all
her finery!

53239.「私に盗めぬ物は なし！\n クイーンの座も 華麗に盗んでみせますわ！\n ドワ:
There's nothing I can't steal! And I will
steal the queen's throne in style! Dwarves,
I'm looking forward to meeting you!

53240.「すべての男は 私に ひれ伏す！\n 彼女に打ちのめされた旅人は 数知れず！\n:
All men bow down to me! Countless a traveler
has been struck down by her! I'm looking for a
servant...

53242.「ふん……。時間のムダね。\n こんなコンテストなんか やるまでもないわ。\n:
What a waste of time. I don't even need to
enter this contest. I'm the one who's going to
be queen.

53243.「そこの あなた！\n いいわね？ あたしを選ぶのよ。\n あたしに ひざまずけ:
Hey, you! Okay? Pick me. You should be honored
to kneel down to me.

53244.「ジュレットの町に舞い降りた 心優しき天使！\n 彼女に頼まれたら 誰も断れない:
A kind-hearted angel descends upon Julet Town!
Who can say no to her when she asks? Can I be
your sister?

53247.「クイーンになれば お友達が増えるかなって。\n だから コンテストに参加してみ:
I thought if I became queen, I would have more
friends. So I decided to enter the contest...
and if I'm good enough, I'd love your support!

53248.「フランクな口調が チャームポイント！\n その明るさで みんなの心を わしづか:
His frank tone of voice is his charm! The person who has captured everyone's hearts with his cheerful personality is coming from heaven
to join us!

53250.「ちっちっち。ちがいまぁーすっ。: Tsk tsk tsk. No, no, no, no, no.

53251.「あたしはぁ アルウェ王妃ちゃん様でーす。\n あたしぃ 予知っ娘だから 結果は:
I am Queen Alwe. I'm the girl with the
foresight, so I know the outcome, but I won't
tell you~.

53252.「すべてのスーパースターが 彼女に嫉妬する\n １００年にひとりの 天才！\n:
The one genius in a century that makes every
superstar jealous! Her dancing is a knockout!

53254.「なぜ あたしが クイーンに選ばれるのか……\n それは あたしが プレシアンナ:
The reason why I'm chosen as Queen is because I'm Prescianna, and a top star doesn't have the word "defeat" in her name. No word for
defeat in the top stars?

53255.「あこがれの いやし系お姉様！\n ああ！ そのムネに抱かれて 眠りたい……！\:
I've always wanted to be your pampered sister!
Ah! I want to sleep in her arms! The dark
horse of this year's competition...

53257.「あっはっはっは！ 他の連中は やせっぽちで\n 全然 女としての魅力が 足りな:
Ha-ha-ha! The rest of them are skinny and not
feminine enough!

53258.「いいかい！ クイーンに必要なのは\n すべてを包み込む 包容力と決まってるのさ:
Listen up! All a queen needs to be is all-
embracing and inclusive! Let's get this match
on the line.

53259.「以上 １０名の美女たちが\n クイーンの座を賭けて コンテストを争います。:
These 10 beauties will compete for the title
of queen.

53260.「果たして 栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will be crowned with glory? It's up to you
to decide!

53261.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n お気に入りの美女は 見つかりましたか？:
What do you think <pc>. Did you find
your favorite beauty?

53262.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n その方から チョコを受け取っ:
If you decide on a beautiful woman whom you think is the best candidate for the queen, please accept the chocolate from her. However,
only one person can receive the chocolates!

53263.「あなたが チョコを受け取った相手に\n あなたの一票が 投じられるのです。\n:
Your vote will be cast for the recipient of
the chocolate. Please think carefully before
making your choice.

53279.「ただいまより 第１回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発表:
We will now announce the results of the 1st
Astor Tia Queen Contest!

53280.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who is worthy of being crowned Queen of our
Chocolat Fontenay Castle?! The results are
in!!

53281.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！: Ladies and gentlemen! Attention on stage!

58803.「選び終わりましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
When you have finished your selection, please
stop by my place for a chat. I'll be outside.
